        {
            "id": 6420030,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 新興(2605)大跌7.11%，報37.25元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新興(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2605-TW</a>)14日13:02股價下跌2.85元，報37.25元，跌幅7.11%，成交13,202張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新興(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2605-TW</a>)所屬產業為航運業，主要業務為船務代理業。拖船駁船業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌2.91%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲8.86%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-236 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+447 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+1 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-684 張</li> <li>融資增減：+977 張</li> <li>融券增減：+115 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
